thread.title: Tammy Bottita
thread.title_full: Skipper (formerly Jetaport) reviewed by Tammy Bottita

author: Tammy Bottita
title: Tammy Bottita
text: Planning wedding has so many moving parts to keep track of and I really appreciate the assistance and great customer service I received from Skipper. Not to mention they didn't make me feel like a pest or silly for all my questions. I will use them again if ever planning another event. Great service!
